      "id": "PopularPost232504",
      "post_content": "@a7141988: Yes, that would work, but as you say, it's really slow. You're talking 9 mana and four cards to exile one creature. Five cards, if you use the [Heartstone](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heartstone).   \n  \nI suggest ditching the mercenaries and using their more powerful cousins- Rebels. [Crib Swap](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crib Swap) + [Lin Sivvi, Defiant Hero](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Lin Sivvi, Defiant Hero) does exactly what you're describing, but with only two cards and six mana. Still pricy, but easily slid into an existing Rebel deck. ",
      "posted_by": "ScissorsLizard",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost232504\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">@a7141988: Yes, that would work, but as you say, it's really slow. You're talking 9 mana and four cards to exile one creature. Five cards, if you use the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Heartstone\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heartstone\">Heartstone</a>. <br/><br/>I suggest ditching the mercenaries and using their more powerful cousins- Rebels. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Crib Swap\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Crib Swap\">Crib Swap</a> +<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\" Lin Sivvi, Defiant Hero\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Lin Sivvi, Defiant Hero\"> Lin Sivvi, Defiant Hero</a> does exactly what you're describing, but with only two cards and six mana. Still pricy, but easily slid into an existing Rebel deck.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '232504'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1310\">ScissorsLizard</span>\r\n                                (3/10/2012 9:07:03 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: lef